    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dedicated project car or a source for parts. The engine currently requires significant repair to be roadworthy, and there are noticeable fluid leaks. The body shows heavy wear, including several dents and areas of rust, while the interior has significant tearing and stains. It will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
      "price": 5500.0,
